#### C1. Full Vote Casting Pipeline Latency
- **Why**: Shows real-world performance, not just isolated crypto operations
- **What**: Time each phase of the vote flow:

| Phase | What It Covers |
|---|---|
| Phase 1: QR Decode + Decrypt | jsQR decode + PBKDF2 + AES-CBC |
| Phase 2: Face Embedding | MediaPipe detect + FaceNet + PCA |
